useful links : https://docling-project.github.io/docling/examples/pictures_description/#describe-pictures-with-smolvlm, https://docling-project.github.io/docling/examples/export_figures/

######### Retrieval stack ############
- Embedder: Qwen/Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B
- Reranker: Qwen/Qwen3-Reranker-0.6B
- Vector DB: Qdrant
- Retrieval: Dense + BM25
- Fusion: RRF
- Chunk size: 220–320 tokens
- Overlap: 40–60 tokens
- Retrieve: 20 dense + 20 BM25
- Rerank: top 20–30
- Send to LLM: top 4–6
- CPU-latency fallback
- keep the same embedder
- replace reranker with BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3 if needed